    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about keeping it spotless and it runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and kept in pristine condition, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message, I'd love to tell you more about it!",
