    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This vehicle exhibits flawless mechanical synchronization, with the variable VANOS system fully serviced and individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous transient response. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Equipped with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain delivers power with surgical precision. Meticulously maintained with an emphasis on thermal management and suspension kinematics, this specimen represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance in a preserved, showroom-state configuration.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
