      "description": "Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle is a true time capsule for the discerning collector. The exterior paintwork is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garaging. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh state; the premium leather is supple and matte, free from any bolster wear or creasing, and every switchgear functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance regimen with a fully documented service history. It drives exactly as it did on day one\u2014tight, quiet, and powerful. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a pristine example that has been pampered from new.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
